NGT transaction implementation from KeplerSynapseNet/src/core/transfer.cpp:

TRANSACTION TOTAL OUTPUT:
  uint64_t Transaction::totalOutput() const {
    uint64_t total = 0;
    for (const auto& outp : outputs) total += outp.amount;
    return total;
  }

SIGNATURE VERIFICATION:
  bool Transaction::verify() const {
    for (const auto& inp : inputs) {
      crypto::Hash256 sigHash = computeHash();
      if (!crypto::verify(sigHash, inp.signature, inp.pubKey)) return false;
    }
    return true;
  }

TRANSFER MANAGER STATE:
  struct TransferManager::Impl {
    database::Database db;
    std::unordered_map<std::string, std::vector<UTXO>> utxoSet;
    std::unordered_map<std::string, Transaction> mempool;
    uint64_t txCounter = 0;
    uint64_t totalSupply_ = 0;
    mutable std::mutex mtx;
  };

KEY FEATURES:
- UTXO ownership enforced: input pubkey must match the UTXO address
- Deterministic reward crediting: rewardId → unique UTXO (idempotent)
- Mempool policy: expiry, size cap, fee checks, deterministic eviction rules
- Block apply/rollback: deterministic UTXO updates on block import/mine
- Single-instance lock: robust fcntl lock, no stale locks after downloads
- --reset-ngt flag: wipes local transfer DB (fixes wrong balances from testing)

P2P TX GOSSIP:
  inv/getdata for mempool sync
  mempool → inv → getdata on peer connect
  tx message type for broadcast
